---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="About">
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About Mainline</h1>

        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-6">
            Mainline is a modern web application built with Astro and powered by Payload CMS,
            combining the best of static site generation with a powerful headless CMS.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Technology Stack</h2>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 not-prose">
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Astro Frontend</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
                <li>• Lightning-fast static site generation</li>
                <li>• Component islands architecture</li>
                <li>• Optimized performance by default</li>
                <li>• Tailwind CSS for styling</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Payload CMS Backend</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
                <li>• Powerful headless CMS</li>
                <li>• REST and GraphQL APIs</li>
                <li>• Cloudflare D1 database</li>
                <li>• R2 storage for media</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Key Features</h2>

          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
            <li>
              <strong>Performance First:</strong> Astro's architecture ensures minimal JavaScript
              and optimal loading times.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Content Management:</strong> Payload CMS provides a flexible and intuitive
              interface for managing content.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Modern Design:</strong> The Mainline theme offers a clean, professional
              design that's fully responsive.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Developer Experience:</strong> Built with TypeScript for type safety and
              better development experience.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
